:"","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"250","text":"• Porfiria","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"278","parent":"250","text":"• Deficiencia de tiamina","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"279","parent":"250","text":"• Trastornos\\Nmetabólicos o\\Nelectrolíticos:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"250","text":"• Hipopotasemia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"281","parent":"250","text":"• Hipofosfatemia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"250","text":"• Hipomagnesemia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"250","text":"• Unión Neuromuscular:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"284","parent":"250","text":"• Miastenia gravis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"285","parent":"250","text":"• Botulismo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"250","text":"• Músculos:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"287","parent":"250","text":"• Neuropatía-miopatía por\\Nenfermedad crítica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"288","parent":"250","text":"• Enfermedad\\Nmitocondrial","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"250","text":"• Rabdomiólisis aguda","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"290","parent":"250","text":"• Polimiositis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"291","parent":"250","text":"• Dermatomiositis","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"292","parent":"0","text":"Referencias:","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"293","parent":"0","text":"(1) Willison HJ, Jacobs BC, van Doorn\\NPA. “Guillain-Barré syndrome.” Lancet.\\N2016;388(10045):717-727.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"294","parent":"0","text":"(2) Yuki N, Hartung HP.\\N“Guillain-Barré syndrome.” N Engl\\NJ Med. 2012;366(24):2294-2304.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"295","parent":"0","text":"(3) Van den Berg B, Walgaard C, Drenthen J, Fokke C,\\NJacobs BC, van Doorn PA. “Guillain-Barré syndrome:\\Npathogenesis, diagnosis, treatment and prognosis.” Nat\\NRev Neurol. 2014;10(8):469-482.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"296","parent":"0","text":"Criterios de Gravedad y\\NPredicción de Ingreso a UCI","g